Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.62,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.63,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.91,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.66,0:01:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[零式系統]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.74,0:01:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把戰況裡出現的一切資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在即時運算後\N得出的龐大預測值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.81,0:01:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接反饋給駕駛員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛艙系統的俗稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這系統甚至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.68,0:01:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會把駕駛員趕進極端狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實現完美的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果連自己的死也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.03,0:01:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界變得混沌的時候裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在了令人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.77,0:01:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為最強兵器的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是飛翼零式和次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十八話\N[莉莉娜女王誕生]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.88,0:02:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的混亂\N招致宇宙衛星的混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗羅姆斐拉財團支配體制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.62,0:02:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星居民們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,組織起武裝集團[白色獠牙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.06,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了解放衛星站起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.13,0:02:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ雖然失去司令官茲巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.67,0:02:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們投入MD\N以武力對抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各地，戰爭的火花\N開始擴散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別正面衝向MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誘引它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去衛星雷射砲的射程距離內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.66,0:03:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們為何要把無意義的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶來宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼…鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.55,0:03:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈看來在戰鬥空域出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，以這艘穿梭機\N不能再接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝，來到這裡就足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後我獨自前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈05的駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也在相信正義而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一部就殲滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的MD?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是鋼彈的力量嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拋掉武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拋掉所有武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果弱者拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就會克服不了我的心而失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱者不要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你仍然沒變啊，張五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.43,0:05:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在維多利亞基地\N有一面之緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時那個女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫路克蕾琪亞‧諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在對你已經毫無懷恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和這個宇宙的廣闊相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.31,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的屈辱根本是小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看來不是來戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想借助你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.22,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想借助所有\N鋼彈駕駛員的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我也愛地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我兩方面都不想傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.77,0:05:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我才想要建立\N和平的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們鋼彈駕駛員\N能了解我的心情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.07,0:05:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯幫助我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那國家滅亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳為何還要戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國家的確滅亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.30,0:06:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國的可貴精神仍然存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想保護那精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人不會想到這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我要走我的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會服從任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.23,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我這邊處理好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:07:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐，你擔心那個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他同樣是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見他變成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.85,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，衛星今後會怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想過很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你擔心甚麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.09,0:07:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要走自己相信的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說那句話的是迪歐你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.09,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼，首先認真找份工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有新工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.07,0:07:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,資源衛星\N招募機動戰士工作人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?希爾妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是溫拿家的資源衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞她的家主被殺後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.58,0:07:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有工程一直被擱置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫拿家的少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，之後的交給…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，卡特爾，很久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是溫拿家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有宏偉的大廈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是由你繼承了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐們正在管理所有資產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.09,0:08:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從我下落不明之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為成為鋼彈駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，你去了哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了地球，和希洛一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了思考應該做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，有答案嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我來找你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.58,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球有很多仁慈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星其實也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家想創造能和平生活的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了那目的，我想保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國的完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的能創造那種世界嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直為了衛星而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥的人我一個就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那種回憶的一個人就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.68,0:09:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，衛星開始戰爭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.11,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後會有更多人死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我或許已經不能再相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一直夢想的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平始終是不會實現的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.30,0:09:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾經犯錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我想不會被原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想豁出一切作出補償
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.90,0:09:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是不抹去名為和平的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為如果失去夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切就會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.58,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漆黑一片的未來\N或許很適合死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡太高尚了，渾身不自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你在找尋鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也想見那傢伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐!那是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳肩負起全世界的命運啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了，我現在就餵你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦…你是特洛瓦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!你不認得我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!去那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會幫你餵牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去幫團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算又帶特洛瓦去戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是這個馬戲團的孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想讓特洛瓦\N再有痛苦回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒有記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那是痛苦的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他不想記起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我…是我的錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦為了糾正我犯的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才犧牲了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然道歉不能彌補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你那樣想，你就別騷擾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為和我們一起的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人是誰…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…認識他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得好親切…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會怎麼辦?還能戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.28,0:13:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，這樣不像我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾見到特洛瓦了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱薩琳，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀眾的入場人數很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日也要努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.74,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會令觀眾一世都不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交戰中的OZ和白色獠牙部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正接近這空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去\N這裡也有可能被牽連
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.77,0:14:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡只有想平靜生活的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的OZ!竟然攻擊衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家去疏散觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他有空的就照顧動物們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好冷…好怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼會來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有事，你放心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會陪著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.84,0:15:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡很危險，快去避難所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟發生甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星附近爆發了機動戰士對戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.59,0:16:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是想平靜生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.42,0:16:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟要有多少人\N犧牲才甘心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再失去寶貴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再失去啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我會保護姐姐妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也已經不想再失去任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.79,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你救了我…救了我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.26,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，今次由我來保護大家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈是為了那樣才造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!就此堅持到援軍來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再讓你們傷害衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.96,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在呼喚我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會有人呼喚你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，那傢伙在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.14,0:18:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊!你遇過那麼痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還打算繼續戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得從前有人這樣說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.09,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照感情行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人類正確的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你無論如何…都要去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.76,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你固執的性格…毫無改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會活著回來啊，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是笨蛋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要令這種事結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，妳準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在世界最高處\N的日子終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都很驚奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我高興得感到同身受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的表情不可以那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要笑得更優雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為妳從今日起\N就是世界的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.62,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的人請聽我講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.29,0:20:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特  從今日起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.19,0:20:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為羅姆斐拉財團的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.13,0:20:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這並非為了羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是為了令世界的紛爭消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立和平的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為這是朝著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和各位一起走的最好的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.74,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,踏出的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.31,0:21:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，請你們拋掉武器\N停止鬥爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位渴望的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.89,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該一定是相同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.82,0:21:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起朝著那未來前進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.83,0:21:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這裡宣佈\N除去世界紛爭之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.56,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國家的門戶之見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確立把地球當作一個國家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[世界國家]宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也虧財團想得出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.26,0:21:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的確能把人心\N吸向羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.23,0:21:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，羅姆斐拉看來沒發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那會有很大的風險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.55,0:22:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
